### Obtener todos los clientes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/client

### Obtener un cliente por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/client/1

### Crear un nuevo cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/api/client
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cliente 1",
  "email": "user@mail.com",
  "phone": "54333444222",
  "issuingCompany": "Company Iss1",
  "receivingCompany": "Company Rec1"
}

### Actualizar un cliente por ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/client/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cliente 1 Actualizado",
  "email": "userupdated@mail.com",
  "phone": "54333444333",
  "issuingCompany": "Company Iss2",
  "receivingCompany": "Company Rec2"
}

### Eliminar un cliente por ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/client/1
